OL,3,CSouth African World Cup player Jayden
OL,4,CAdams dies aged 25
OL,6,FSouth Africa midfielder Jayden Adams
OL,7,Fhas died, a government minister has
OL,8,Fconfirmed.
OL,10,FThe 25-year-old featured in all three
OL,11,Fof his country's group matches at the
OL,12,FWorld Cup last month.
OL,14,FAdams, who played his club football
OL,15,Ffor Pretoria side Mamelodi Sundowns,
OL,16,Fwas an unused substitute as South
OL,17,FAfrica exited the tournament in a last-
OL,18,F32 defeat to co-hosts Canada on June
OL,19,F28.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
