OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1783885299
OL,3,CSouth African World Cup player Jayden
OL,4,CAdams dies aged 25
OL,6,FGayton McKenzie, South Africa's
OL,7,Fminister of sport, arts and culture,
OL,8,Fsaid in a statement reported by a
OL,9,Fnumber of news outlets: "It is with
OL,10,Fprofound shock and a heavy heart that
OL,11,FI have learnt of the passing of Jayden
OL,12,FAdams.
OL,14,F"South African football has lost one
OL,15,Fof its brightest young talents, and
OL,16,Four nation mourns alongside his
OL,17,Ffamily, his team-mates and the
OL,18,Fmillions of supporters who watched him
OL,19,Fgrow from a promising academy prospect
OL,20,Finto a full Bafana Bafana
OL,21,Finternational."
OL,26,@qD@YOUvD@AOU}D@OO]
