OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1783885299
OL,3,CSouth African World Cup player Jayden
OL,4,CAdams dies aged 25
OL,6,FAdams played in South Africa's games
OL,7,Fagainst Mexico, the Czech Republic and
OL,8,FSouth Korea. The game against the
OL,9,FCzech Republic came the day after his
OL,10,Fgrandmother Marianna died.
OL,12,FHis players' union said, "death has
OL,13,Fcruelly stolen one of our own".
OL,15,FA statement added: "The South African
OL,16,FFootball Players Union (SAFPU) is
OL,17,Fdevastated by the untimely passing of
OL,18,FMamelodi Sundowns and Bafana Bafana
OL,19,Fmidfielder, Jayden Adams.
OL,26,@tD@ZOUuD@^O]wD@TOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
