OL,3,CSouth African World Cup player Jayden
OL,4,CAdams dies aged 25
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,F"Jayden had only recently represented
OL,12,FSouth Africa at the 2026 FIFA World
OL,13,FCup, carrying the hopes of the nation
OL,14,Fwith pride, courage and distinction.
OL,15,FHis passing is an immeasurable loss to
OL,16,Fhis family, teammates, clubs, the
OL,17,Ffootball fraternity and the country at
OL,18,Flarge.
OL,26,@sD@AOU
