OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1783885299
OL,3,CSouth African World Cup player Jayden
OL,4,CAdams dies aged 25
OL,6,F"We extend our deepest condolences to
OL,7,Fthe Adams family, Mamelodi Sundowns,
OL,8,FStellenbosch FC, Bafana Bafana and all
OL,9,Fthose whose lives he touched.
OL,11,F"South African football has lost a
OL,12,Fgifted player, a proud servant of the
OL,13,Fgame and a young life that still had
OL,14,Fso much to offer."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUvD@RO]
